<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Site Under Construction</title>
  <style>
    body {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background-image: url('/images/background.webp');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }
    .container {
      text-align: center;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      max-width: 400px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .logo {
      width: 400px;
      height: auto;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }
    .logo img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      object-fit: contain;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Beauty & Health Studio Logo">
    </div>
    <h1>Web stranica u izradi</h1>
    <p>Naša web stranica je trenutno u izradi. Vredno radimo na tome da vam pružimo bolje iskustvo!</p>
    <div class="contact-info">
      <p>Za više informacija o tretmanima, molimo vas da nas kontaktirate na: <br> <strong>062 219 870</strong></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
